paragraphs.title: Register the Custom SplitterUDF
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.analysis.FunctionRegistry
import com.advancedspark.sql.functions.SplitterUDF

sqlContext.udf.register("splitter", SplitterUDF)

sqlContext.sql(s"""REFRESH TABLE MOVIES""")
val moviesDF = sqlContext.sql(s"""select movieId, title, genres, splitter(genres, "|", 0) from movies limit 10""")

z.show(moviesDF)
